## WorkerServiceProtocol.InitializedMessage interface

This message is sent by the worker to the main thread. No data is sent. Receiving this message confirms that the worker has started successfully.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
interface InitializedMessage extends ServiceMessage 
```
